[[File:Hideout_256.png|right]]The '''Hideout''' is a building in [[Lord of Ultima]]. It allows safe storage of resources, preventing them from being reported by Scouts or plundered. Its capacity can be increased if built beside woods.

'''Requirements:''' [[Town Hall]] Level 2

